{"title":"海潮","authors":["刘原"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":12,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"海潮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过渔村"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夕阳已随婆娑椰树沉入海面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"波光粼粼的晚霞在水里漂浮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轰鸣入耳的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍然是泛动泡沫的雪白浪花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是荡漾羽翼的蔚蓝呼唤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驰近的帆船转过礁石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消失在黄昏的港湾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海滩无比宁静"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"椰树如少女含笑伫立"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在海风里飘舞着秀发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛等待某一种启示"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从悠远的海域"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总涌来滚滚的吞噬沙粒的海潮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它涌到颀长的椰树脚下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却总是后退后退"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后又一丝不苟地涌来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过渔村"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走在这弥漫浓郁情绪的气氛里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这追求的执著与被追求的含蓄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我开始打量村落的盏盏灯火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打量夜色笼罩的渊博的海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打量月亮  以及月光"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}